  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-01-21",
    "date": "2021-05-10T16:43:00Z",
    "text": "David Dorn Act of 2021\n\nThis bill increases criminal penalties for rioting and related offenses (e.g., inciting a riot).\n\nSpecifically, the bill increases the maximum prison term from 5 to 10 years. Additionally, if a fine is imposed for an offense, the bill sets a minimum fine amount of $1,000."
  },
